DOGS POISONED- Between May 1 and Octo- ber 31, the Cairo City Police have
                        poisoned 1,488 stray dogs. They are distributed as follows:- Esbekieh, 184;
                        Abdeen, 93; Gema lieb, 70; Mousky, 73; Waili, 87; Zeitoun, 90; Matarieh, 86;
                        Khalifa, 139; Saida Zenab, 69; Bab el-Sharieb, 83; Darb el-Ahmar, 76;
                        Koubbeh, 10; Ain el-Shams, 81; Boulac, 107; Shoubra, 105; Helouan, 50;
                        Ghezireh, 67; Old Cairo, 18.
